{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This games main focus is its silent narrative, meaning the story is told without text or dialogue. An active plot unfolds through scenes using characters expressions, music, and visual language. Exploration, Combat, and Boss fights are between the brief narrative scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally, the games tutorials and menus use no text either. So, with the exception of the game's title/logo there are no languages present in the game and can be enjoyed without understanding English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story Summary</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A woman longs for her lost husband when the storm rolls in. Then strange figures attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image1.jpg?t=1736313892\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image3.jpg?t=1736313892\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image4.jpg?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More of these soldiers come in forcing her to flee into the woods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image7.jpg?t=1736313892\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image8.jpg?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image5.jpg?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There she meets a strange person that she seems to recognize, though he does not recognize her. The two of them continue to run from the storm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image6.jpg?t=1736313892\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image9.jpg?t=1736313892\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image10.jpg?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Coming up the neighboring city seeking refuge an unexpected someone is waiting there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store_image11.jpg?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time a block correctly to parry an enemy's attack and reduce their stamina.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store-Gif-1.gif?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When an enemy's stamina run out, they will be briefly stunned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store-Gif-3.gif?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Avoid unblockable attacks by dodging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/Store-Gif-2.gif?t=1736313892\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeating enemy's and exploring will accumulate EXP and level up the player character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expected playtime for this game should be around 3 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736313892","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736313892","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/515b0591abb935c01486a10549e38653afe83ae8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736313892","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/515b0591abb935c01486a10549e38653afe83ae8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736313892","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3302790,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This games main focus is its silent narrative, meaning the story is told without text or dialogue. An active plot unfolds through scenes using characters expressions, music, and visual language. Exploration, Combat, and Boss fights are between the brief narrative scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally, the games tutorials and menus use no text either. So, with the exception of the game's title/logo there are no languages present in the game and can be enjoyed without understanding English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story Summary</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A woman longs for her lost husband when the storm rolls in. Then strange figures attack.</p><p class=\"bb_para